---
import { Layers, Sparkles, Workflow, Languages } from "@lucide/astro"
import aboutImg from "../assets/about.svg";
---

<section class="about-wrapper flex justify-center px-4 py-8 sm:px-8 " id="about" data-animate="section">
		<div class="about-panel relative isolate flex w-full max-w-6xl flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-[36px] bg-(--surface-base) text-(--ink-body) shadow-(--shadow-elevated)" data-animate-target>
		<div class="about-pattern" aria-hidden="true"></div>
		<div class="about-highlight" aria-hidden="true"></div>

		<div class="grid gap-10 p-8 sm:gap-12 sm:p-12 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.02fr)_minmax(0,0.98fr)] lg:items-center lg:gap-14 xl:p-16">
			<div class="space-y-6 lg:space-y-7">
				<span class="inline-flex w-fit items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-(--brand-primary-outline) bg-(--brand-primary-soft) px-4 py-1.5 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide text-(--brand-primary-dark)">
					<span class="inline-block h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-(--brand-primary)"></span>
					コンセプト
				</span>

				<h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold leading-[1.1] tracking-tight text-(--ink-strong) sm:text-4xl lg:text-[2.65rem]">
					<span class="text-(--brand-primary-strong)">「機能性」</span>と
					<span class="text-(--brand-primary-strong)">「使いやすさ」</span>を両立した、ビジネス成果につながるWebエンジニアリングを
				</h2>

				<div class="about-copy space-y-4 text-base text-(--ink-body) sm:text-lg">
					<p>
ユーザーが迷わず目的にたどり着けるシンプルで効率的なUIを重視しています。
デザインから実装、改善まで一貫して対応し、使いやすさとビジネス成果の両立を目指します。
					</p>
					<p>
管理ダッシュボードやマッチングプラットフォームなどの開発経験を通じて、再利用性の高いコンポーネント設計や効率的なワークフローを実践してきました。
					</p>
				</div>

				<ul class="about-highlights grid gap-4 pt-2 sm:grid-cols-2">
					<li class="about-highlight-card" data-animate-child>
						<span class="icon-badge">
							<Layers class="icon" />
						</span>
						<div>
							<h3>設計から実装・運用まで一貫対応</h3>
							<p>要件定義からリリース後の改善まで対応し、継続的な価値提供を実現します。</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="about-highlight-card" data-animate-child>
						<span class="icon-badge">
							<Sparkles class="icon" />
						</span>
						<div>
							<h3>再利用性と拡張性を考慮した設計</h3>
							<p>デザインシステムとブランドトークンを活用し、長期的に成長できるプロダクトを構築します。</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="about-highlight-card" data-animate-child>
						<span class="icon-badge">
							<Workflow class="icon" />
						</span>
						<div>
							<h3>ユーザー視点のUI/UX設計</h3>
							<p>プロトタイプ検証を重ね、直感的に使えるインターフェースを追求します。</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="about-highlight-card" data-animate-child>
						<span class="icon-badge">
							<Languages class="icon" />
						</span>
						<div>
							<h3>多言語・多文化環境での開発経験</h3>
							<p>トルコ語・英語・日本語でのコミュニケーションにより、グローバルな開発チームとも円滑に協働。</p>
						</div>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div class="about-media">
					<div class="about-media-frame">
								<div class="media-placeholder" style={`background-image: url('${aboutImg.src}');`} aria-hidden="true">
									<span>イラスト/画像</span>
								</div>
							</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.about-panel {
		position: relative;
	}

	.about-pattern {
		position: absolute;
		inset: 0;
		background-image: linear-gradient(
				to right,
				color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface-outline) 36%, transparent) 1px,
				transparent 1px
			),
			linear-gradient(
				to bottom,
				color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface-outline) 36%, transparent) 1px,
				transparent 1px
			);
		background-size: 60px 60px;
		opacity: 0.45;
		pointer-events: none;
		z-index: 0;
	}

	.about-highlight {
		position: absolute;
		width: 320px;
		height: 320px;
		bottom: -160px;
		left: -140px;
		background: radial-gradient(
			circle,
			color-mix(in srgb, var(--brand-primary) 38%, transparent) 0%,
			transparent 70%
		);
		pointer-events: none;
		z-index: 0;
	}

	.about-panel > .grid,
	.about-panel > .grid * {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.about-highlights {
		list-style: none;
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0;
	}

	.about-highlight-card {
		display: flex;
		gap: 0.9rem;
		padding: 1rem 1.1rem;
		border-radius: 22px;
		border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface-outline) 80%, transparent);
		background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface-base) 96%, transparent);
		box-shadow: 0 18px 42px rgba(12, 18, 32, 0.06);
		transition: transform 0.35s ease, border-color 0.35s ease, box-shadow 0.35s ease;
	}

	.about-highlight-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-6px);
		border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--brand-primary) 52%, var(--surface-outline));
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-accent);
	}

	.about-highlight-card h3 {
		margin: 0 0 0.3rem;
		font-size: 1rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--ink-strong);
	}

	.about-highlight-card p {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 0.92rem;
		line-height: 1.5;
		color: var(--ink-muted);
	}

	.icon-badge {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		height: 2.5rem;
		width: 2.5rem;
		border-radius: 999px;
		background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--brand-primary) 20%, var(--surface-base));
		color: var(--brand-primary-dark);
		box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
	}

	.icon {
		width: 1.35rem;
		height: 1.35rem;
	}

	.about-media {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.about-media-frame {
		position: relative;
		width: min(100%, 440px);
		padding: 1.6rem;
		border-radius: 28px;
		border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface-outline) 72%, transparent);
		background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface-base) 98%, transparent);
		box-shadow: 0 30px 90px rgba(8, 12, 24, 0.12);
	}

	.media-placeholder {
		display: block;
		height: 420px; /* increased to avoid cutting faces for illustrations */
		border-radius: 24px;
		background-size: contain; /* keep full svg visible */
		background-position: center;
		background-repeat: no-repeat;
		border: none;
		background-color: transparent;
	}

	.media-placeholder > * {
		display: none;
	}

	.media-caption {
		margin-top: 1.25rem;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: var(--ink-subtle);
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	@media (max-width: 1024px) {
		.about-wrapper {
			padding-block: 2.5rem;
		}

		.about-panel {
			border-radius: 28px;
		}

		.about-media-frame {
			padding: 1.4rem;
		}

		.media-placeholder {
			height: 300px;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		.about-wrapper {
			padding-inline: 1rem;
		}

		.about-panel {
			border-radius: 22px;
		}

		.about-panel .grid {
			gap: 2.75rem;
		}

		.about-media-frame {
			padding: 1.1rem;
		}

		.media-placeholder {
			height: 260px;
			border-radius: 20px;
		}
	}
</style>
